{"tid":623724,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS4 Pro Club D1 VPL比賽球隊招有能力球員(Full time)","createTime":"2018-04-10T08:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T12:51:46.000Z","uid":181461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6b1e6870cb32feebdbb405a413633b03f011847c","tid":623724,"uid":181461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:37:17.000Z","msg":"本球會為D1球會 以vpl比賽為目標 現正積極備戰下屆比賽 同時亦會因應隊員情況 報名其他比賽 儘可能為球員參加更多不同類型比賽<br />\n球隊打法 簡單 快速 有明確戰術<br />\n現招募 前場多面手1名 能打前場不同位置<br />\n後防球員 cb為主 能客串閘位更佳<br />\n<br />\n開波時間:星期一至五 10點半至1點(按情況或會延長）<br />\n             星期六/日 因應情況安排 <br />\n基本需求:每星期起碼能訓練三日<br />\n團隊型球員 跟戰術指示 接受意見 不埋怨隊友 態度積極<br />\n<br />\n如有興趣參加比賽 而自覺有能力者 請在以下留言或直接加telegram kaikai0621<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c153d49319512a303fb3112b60e4839d308dec","tid":623724,"uid":181461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T09:26:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f1b966c035f2063e926831ae1dbc2405b7d19a0","tid":623724,"uid":181461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:12:08.000Z","msg":"如好憎隊友打天才波 覺得自己懷才不遇<br />\n呢道歡迎你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e998aba0c37c6dfbe6c054155d8145b143f6dbe","tid":623724,"uid":181461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T13:28:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9749b2a560d75d3f7ff85f9072ca9f186b60ff6d","tid":623724,"uid":181461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T05:44:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2073bf0e44fd67d273a6d2f78c365860dfd10bec","tid":623724,"uid":181461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:06:26.000Z","msg":"推<img sr